Hey Emily (sorry in and out of meetings) you would want to place this in your coded file to include those. Ideally if youâ€™re including header and footer elements, you would want to place it like so:
```&lt;html lang="{{ html_lang }}" {{ html_lang_dir }}&gt;
  &lt;head&gt;
    &lt;meta charset="utf-8"&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;{{ page_meta.html_title }}&lt;/title&gt;
    &lt;meta name="description" content="{{ page_meta.meta_description }}"&gt;
    {{ standard_header_includes }}
  &lt;/head&gt;
  &lt;body&gt;
     {% include "design-manger/path/to/my_header.html" %}

        REST OF HTML CONTENT HERE

     {% include "design-manger/path/to/my_footer.html" %}
  &lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;```
